{"tid":102612,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"關於男友既ex 點樣可以睇開啲","createTime":"2017-01-31T17:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T07:10:14.000Z","uid":7421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23e5ec2e7b1453bf9dc9773a98cb7f452d031c6e","tid":102612,"uid":7421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"男友有個拍左十幾年拖既ex<br />\n佢係比人飛既 有第三者 但散左之後男方keep住金公試 生活上照顧佢<br />\n<br />\n識左我之後 佢終於搞清楚同ex既關係 然後我地一齊左<br />\n但久唔久ex就聯絡佢 男友話唔可能叫佢唔搵<br />\n<br />\n每次都搞到吵大鑊<br />\n男友話只當佢係識左十幾年既好友<br />\n反而話我唔比交友自由佢 又話我唔信佢<br />\n我應該點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 佢地瞞住我見過一次面 但比我識穿左"},{"pid":"efb885e2ecb4b1a4ce9f901f35fdae00a9b3d9c6","tid":102612,"uid":75438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:10:52.000Z","msg":"你有無frd底既ex 有既試下做同樣既野比佢感受下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c601e00aed8bdf2d60551325e36b5076e2adc8b","tid":102612,"uid":7421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有無frd底既ex 有既試下做同樣既野比佢感受下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有 但因為自己有男友 同埋ex都有新女友 所以唔搞住人了"},{"pid":"d7ef29b26b37e3a87aaef2f048528dd66edc92f3","tid":102612,"uid":81222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:23:11.000Z","msg":"我男友O8... 諗係佢啲ex 永遠睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7335df877f1081e18e4d6de4fab517f1945eb951","tid":102612,"uid":12219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:23:56.000Z","msg":"我個時要男朋友unfriend, unfollow 曬Ex Facebook, ig<br />\n之後佢ex send msg煩我男朋友仲有幫我鬧返佢同block曬佢ex d contact<br />\n一齊左男朋友就要諗下你感受，唔係唔信，而係你會唔開心<br />\n一係唔好見ex 一係就帶埋你出去見"},{"pid":"2600b50bb5064f3396e0cbe4e5c09970f4f06757","tid":102612,"uid":33356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:25:34.000Z","msg":"瞞住你見面唔係已經好